{"tid":773072,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"呢度有冇人聽毛不易?","createTime":"2018-08-09T08:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T17:51:02.000Z","uid":30195,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c68f1caf68dda0bdd6340b9ebbbc60d806c2959c","tid":773072,"uid":30195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"幾個月前youtube自己播歌, 我就冇睇住部電腦, 突然間有隻歌覺得好好聽<br />\n<br />\n像我這樣的人:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rexoYoF_4wY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrexoYoF_4wY&d=IStaSTnqwvqTOOLvOITvLE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a4ada6af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rexoYoF_4wY</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>像我這樣迷茫的人 像我這樣尋找的人 像我這樣碌碌無為的人 你還見過多少人</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住開始搵佢其他歌聽, 先發現佢係大陸嗰啲濕鳩節目出黎 (明日之子)<br />\n<br />\n佢唔高音, 音域應該都唔闊, 但係把聲好舒服<br />\n<br />\n值得留意既係, 佢啲歌既歌詞全部自己填, 當中最令人震撼或者成名作就係呢首:-<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消愁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZHGN3ViWrns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZHGN3ViWrns&d=IStaSTnqwvqTOOLvOITvLE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=553e8c2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZHGN3ViWrns</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>一杯敬自由 一杯敬死亡 寬恕我的平凡 驅散了迷惘</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近出左專輯, 有首歌想同大家分享, 係講媽媽既, 首歌叫做<br />\n<br />\n一葷一素 (youtube搵唔到link唔好意思):<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtaker.com/video/svb5-decab9f651be4128bdedf0aecffe34e685.html.%E6%AF%9B%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93-45-%E4%B8%80%E8%91%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%B4%A0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtaker.com%2Fvideo%2Fsvb5-decab9f651be4128bdedf0aecffe34e685.html.%25E6%25AF%259B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%2593-45-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2591%25B7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25B4%25A0.html&d=IStaSTnqwvqTOOLvOITvLE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=6b4ad28e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtaker.com/video/svb5-decab9f651be4128bdedf0aecffe34e685.html.%E6%AF%9B%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93-45-%E4%B8%80%E8%91%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%B4%A0.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>太年輕的人 他總是不滿足<br />\n固執地不願停下 遠行的腳步<br />\n望著高高的天走了長長的路<br />\n忘了回頭看 她有沒有哭</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他歌都好好聽, 雖然曲風冇太大變化, 但係佢總係可以將複製既感情, 用最簡單既文字描繪, 每首歌都好純粹<br />\n<br />\n希望大家有時間可以聽下咀嚼下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf7dac3ca82e7d566249aa879cc31a9eb61bdfc","tid":773072,"uid":154872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:21:21.000Z","msg":"冇聽<br />\n<br />\n但幫你推"},{"pid":"1c2f0ad458138638711d39d8698da06651128a98","tid":773072,"uid":61926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"大部分聽過 像我這樣的人 消愁 等 呢幾首唔錯"},{"pid":"61fbf5221209063efd3626e204f526f818f40d1d","tid":773072,"uid":30195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bf7dac3ca82e7d566249aa879cc31a9eb61bdfc","tid":773072,"uid":154872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:21:21.000Z","msg":"冇聽<br />\n<br />\n但幫你推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"多謝你 有時間都聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a0477f1adebbf6ff00d41101f42809d0fc6ce4","tid":773072,"uid":30195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c2f0ad458138638711d39d8698da06651128a98","tid":773072,"uid":61926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"大部分聽過 像我這樣的人 消愁 等 呢幾首唔錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:34:16.000Z","msg":"有首都係新碟既歌, 叫做給你給我, 同像我這樣的人、消愁唔同風格<br />\n<br />\n行溫馨路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n給你我義無反顧的長長和久久<br />\n給我你多年以後仍握緊的手<br />\n給你成熟 你給我遷就<br />\n會不會就這樣白了頭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DTZzyWGTS-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDTZzyWGTS-A&d=IStaSTnqwvqTOOLvOITvLE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2329fbe3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DTZzyWGTS-A</a>"},{"pid":"ef2424dff2