6a7b","tid":773072,"uid":68783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"無問<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821a22a6dada9fcad5b3749b90454895d28fbf0e","tid":773072,"uid":9251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:36:39.000Z","msg":"終於搵到有人聽毛不易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢啲歌真係好好聽 好有才華 份人重好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw新專入面嘅一葷一素都好好聽 講佢媽媽 好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc8b411d47cf2c4ac29c9f718a4446eb92834ab","tid":773072,"uid":171309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68f1caf68dda0bdd6340b9ebbbc60d806c2959c","tid":773072,"uid":30195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"幾個月前youtube自己播歌, 我就冇睇住部電腦, 突然間有隻歌覺得好好聽<br />\n<br />\n像我這樣的人:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rexoYoF_4wY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrexoYoF_4wY&d=IStaSTnqwvqTOOLvOITvLE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a4ada6af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rexoYoF_4wY</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>像我這樣迷茫的人 像我這樣尋找的人 像我這樣碌碌無為的人 你還見過多少人</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住開始搵佢其他歌聽, 先發現佢係大陸嗰啲濕鳩節目出黎 (明日之子)<br />\n<br />\n佢唔高音, 音域應該都唔闊, 但係把聲好舒服<br />\n<br />\n值得留意既係, 佢啲歌既歌詞全部自己填, 當中最令人震撼或者成名作就係呢首:-<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消愁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZHGN3ViWrns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZHGN3ViWrns&d=IStaSTnqwvqTOOLvOITvLE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=553e8c2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZHGN3ViWrns</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>一杯敬自由 一杯敬死亡 寬恕我的平凡 驅散了迷惘</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近出左專輯, 有首歌想同大家分享, 係講媽媽既, 首歌叫做<br />\n<br />\n一葷一素 (youtube搵唔到link唔好意思):<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtaker.com/video/svb5-decab9f651be4128bdedf0aecffe34e685.html.%E6%AF%9B%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93-45-%E4%B8%80%E8%91%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%B4%A0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtaker.com%2Fvideo%2Fsvb5-decab9f651be4128bdedf0aecffe34e685.html.%25E6%25AF%259B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%2593-45-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2591%25B7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25B4%25A0.html&d=IStaSTnqwvqTOOLvOITvLE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=6b4ad28e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtaker.com/video/svb5-decab9f651be4128bdedf0aecffe34e685.html.%E6%AF%9B%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93-45-%E4%B8%80%E8%91%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%B4%A0.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>太年輕的人 他總是不滿足<br />\n固執地不願停下 遠行的腳步<br />\n望著高高的天走了長長的路<br />\n忘了回頭看 她有沒有哭</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他歌都好好聽, 雖然曲風冇太大變化, 但係佢總係可以將複製既感情, 用最簡單既文字描繪, 每首歌都好純粹<br />\n<br />\n希望大家有時間可以聽下咀嚼下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:44:00.000Z","msg":"我搵到1300 ww 但果個post爆左"},{"pid":"417086d470b600df5a75266031abcd9d38215316","tid":773072,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:37:52.000Z","msg":"唔開心<br />\n毛毛原來係護旗手<br />\n仲話支持香港警察<br />\n雖然有可能係唔出聲會被封殺<br />\n但係都係唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd52cb49bc80d2e9426691485bf11e13d111bf82","tid":773072,"uid":198571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"417086d470b600df5a75266031abcd9d38215316","tid":773072,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:37:52.000Z","msg":"唔開心<br />\n毛毛原來係護旗手<br />\n仲話支持香港警察<br />\n雖然有可能係唔出聲會被封殺<br />\n但係都係唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"我都因為咁sad咗一排/_\\但諗諗下又覺得大陸明星表態係無可厚非"}]}